{"tid":2323542,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"尼古拉斯基治將主持Netflix新節目《粗口的歷史》","createTime":"2020-12-13T08:55:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T14:21:02.000Z","uid":41343,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"96b2b1e552864ec05d515023e92ab71a262282c5","tid":2323542,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T08:55:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4argVWl8AAE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4argVWl8AAE&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mTC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=80071221\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4argVWl8AAE</a><br />\n<br />\nNetflix 這次將推出紀錄片節目《髒話的歷史》（History Of Swear Words），還大陣仗找來奧斯卡金獎影帝「尼可拉斯凱吉」擔任主持人，以幽默詼諧的方式一次帶你認識各種髒話的起源！<br />\n<br />\n《髒話的歷史》未來將會在六集的集數當中帶各位了解常掛在嘴邊的 fuck、shit、damn 等詞彙到底都是從哪來，還會邀請許多藝人、歷史與詞源學家一起參與討論，內容估計會很新鮮有趣！"},{"pid":"95af01f896eeb865bc770f4ced18917629ae019b","tid":2323542,"uid":330068,"like":34,"dislike":3,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T09:01:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rfOkUBH.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrfOkUBH.gif&h=fd58c1d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e8b0f70900630bf5ce029e10a0af914c0f48551","tid":2323542,"uid":77180,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T09:17:20.000Z","msg":"快d光復nic cage<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac797552eb24513589c55189e02525db1fb54987","tid":2323542,"uid":3423,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T12:45:50.000Z","msg":"自從上次係灣仔見過佢後，就再冇見過佢上電視"},{"pid":"e0d8de009c48d2eaaf56b6818ba8e4e5c12b9469","tid":2323542,"uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T14:55:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.gifer.com/GJnq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gifer.com%2FGJnq.gif&h=a0a9abf9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a3d808368db5ef3ee1c6a0d9917adaaa4f5f7bd","tid":2323542,"uid":61372,"like":2,"dis